    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自Synth Riders的创作者带来<strong>FINAL FURY</strong>，一款重新定义进入擂台体验的VR格斗游戏。与银河系最强大的战士对抗——无论是离线还是通过rollback netcode与全世界对战。这可不是简单的按键大战。每一拳、每一个格挡、每一个特殊攻击都由你来掌控。[ /p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><strong>FINAL FURY</strong>不仅仅是一款格斗游戏——它是做得正确的<strong>VR</strong>格斗游戏。[ /p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‎ㅤ</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.poster.avif?t=1764605136\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.webm?t=1764605136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊  <strong>感受战斗的激情</strong>，亲自走进擂台。这是第一人称的对决！  <br><br>🥊<strong>创新的VR战斗</strong>，结合了街机格斗机制和身体动作游戏。  <br><br>🥊<strong>不断扩展的角色阵容</strong>，每个角色都有独特的招式、场地和个性，适应你的游戏风格！  <br><br>🥊<strong>单人训练</strong>，与一位专为挑战你而设计的AI对战。刻苦训练，挥洒汗水，提升你的耐力，然后争取星际荣耀！  <br><br>🥊<strong>在线竞技</strong>，支持跨平台对战和rollback netcode。准备好迎接挑战，没有借口！  <br><br>🥊 <strong>全力以赴</strong>，在战斗中挥洒汗水！  <br><br>🥊<strong>激动人心的原声音乐</strong>，由Zardonic（SUPERHOT: MIND CONTROL DELETE）创作。[ /p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/62d1b84975d2923daa09e15d7910965b.avif?t=1764605136\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为战士</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FINAL FURY</strong>不仅仅是选择一个角色并学习他的招式——你要成为那个角色！感受肾上腺素，当你在沉浸式VR战斗中释放你的FINAL FURY，你就是英雄。无论是冲锋、玩脚步战术，还是取消动作来取得胜利，<strong>FINAL FURY</strong>的技能曲线易于上手，难以精通。[ /p]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/116ae908672bf5fc87aff3e725974675.poster.avif?t=1764605136\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/116ae908672bf5fc87aff3e725974675.webm?t=1764605136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>电影级对决</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验激烈的战斗，在第一人称视角中交锋，然后通过第三人称视角的电影剪辑，感受强力的终结技和抓取动作。所有这一切都围绕你展开，同时伴随着Zardonic（SUPERHOT: MIND CONTROL DELETE）带来的充满肾上腺素的音乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/3d62f0a137c7990d5a6db285f77668a9.avif?t=1764605136\" width=616 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入官方的<strong>FINAL FURY</strong> Discord，了解更多关于社区赛事、最新的FINAL FURY新闻以及来自开发团队的第一手资讯！这场战斗才刚刚开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/4b3d440b3a6e4bb311cf6c5c6abb28c0.webp?t=1764605136\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
